The crowning of national assembly speaker Justin Muturi as Mount Kenya spokesperson continues to elicit mixed feelings from a section of leaders in that region. several sitting and former governors from MT. Kenya has dismissed the move to make Muturi the sole voice from the mountain saying it was done irregularly and without consultation. the leaders further said that one of them will be running for the country's top seat after president Uhuru Kenyatta exits in 2022. Emmanuel too reports.